name: iPollo Metaverse Pass by Nano Labs

metadata.name: iPollo Metaverse Pass
metadata.description: Nano Labs, is an avid metaverse explorer, which counts many years of investment in research and development.Their mission is to provide ubiquitous computing power to the Metaverse computing network with their fabless logic-memory integrated circuits. It provides energy-efficient computing infrastructure (iPollo) and solutions for the Metaverse digital world (iPolloverse). iPollo Miner series products are well recognized by the industry. iPolloverse being a decentralized rendering network, it encourages the contribution of computing, storage, and networking resources all over the world for metaverse in a permissionless way.
